description: Götenehus Group AB engages in the development and construction of housing and other types of accommodation. The company is headquartered in Goetene, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 148 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2006-11-23. The Company’s primary products are terrace houses. The Group consists of three business areas: Projects, Prefabricated Wooden Houses and Other. Projects business area comprises production of new terrace houses and project development of multifamily houses. Prefabricated Wooden Houses business area engages in marketing and construction of independent villas and recreational cottages. Villas are marketed under Gotenehus brand while cottages under Varsasvillan. Other business area consists of subsidiary Gotene Traindustri AB, which operates a planing mill and production of wood briquettes. The Company’s market concentrates in Skaraborg, Gothenburg, Stockholm and Skane regions.
name: Gotenehus Group AB
